The paper deals with the analysis of success probability and area spectral efficiency in downlink multiple-antenna (MIMO) heterogeneous cellular networks (HetNets), which involves the use of information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), mathematical analysis (cs.MA), signal processing (cs.SI), and game theory (cs.GT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
